     Created: 2026-03-06
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Office theme. Inspired by Microsoft Office
         2021/365 light theme with white surfaces, soft gray borders, and Microsoft
         blue (#0078D4) accent colors for a familiar productivity-app look.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in OfficeTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Light/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

